e monitoring and temperature measurement. The parallel support hold a stable and fast non-contact human body infrared temperature measurement (frontal temperature).</p>		\n			<h2>Key Highlight</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										8-inch LCD touch display \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Thermal IR camera \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Wi-Fi interface \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										100,000 face database \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Anti-backlight \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Liveness detection \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Non-contact temperature measurement\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Supports recognition with masks \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Less than 1 second recognition \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										99.99% recognition accuracy \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/uface-1-232x300.png\" alt=\"uface-1\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/uface-2-106x300.png\" alt=\"uface-2\" /></figure>			\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/anviz-logo-01.png\" title=\"anviz logo-01\" alt=\"anviz logo-01\" />											\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"356\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-e1588906193309-1024x356.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-e1588906193309-1024x356.png 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-e1588906193309-300x104.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-e1588906193309-768x267.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-e1588906193309.png 1117w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>BIOMETRIC</h2>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"179\" src=\"http://localhos