3b0r0a1qv06ax116mep5rmfft337m03o92lkg.png\" title=\"cost-effective-01\" alt=\"cost-effective-01\" />											\n		<p>Most Cost-effective Solution</p>		\n			<h2>MEGVII MINGJI-MINI</h2>		\n		<p>MEGVII MingJi is based on face detection technology and dual sensing via infrared cameras and visible light. Through this technology, MingJi is capable to swiftly identify people who may have elevated body temperatures, and locate them in the crowd using available body and facial information. </p>		\n			<h2>Key Highlight</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Easy setup - Plug in and play with TV / Monitor HDMI display\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Light weight - All setup equipment together in a 10kg backpack for portal purpose\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Dual camera - IR light for body temperature measuring and RGB light for facial image capture and monitor\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Accurate temperature measurement for 3 to 4 people at the same time\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Fever and not wearing mask alert\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Gender and age range classification\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Historical data storage up to 100,000 persons \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Staff enrollment for easy track back \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/mingji-3-01.png\" alt=\"mingji-3-01\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/mingji-2-01.png\" alt=\"mingji-2-01\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/mingji-1-01.png\" alt=\"mingji-1-01\" /></figure>			\n			<h2>UFACE THERMAL FACIAL SCANNER</h2>		\n		<p>UFACE Thermal Scanner is a high performance, high reliability and high accuracy face recognition products that support 1:1 and 1:N mode of face recognition. It uses Excelitas Thermal IR Sensors for motion detection, presence monitoring and temperature measurement. The parallel support hold a stable and fast non-contact human body infrared temperature measurement (frontal temperature).</p>		\n			<h2>Key Highlight</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										8-inch LCD touch display \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Thermal IR camera \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Wi-Fi interface \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										100,000 face database \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Anti-backlight \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Liveness detection \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Non-contact temperature measurement\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Supports recognition with masks \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Less than 1 second recognition \n									</li>\n								<li >\n										99.99% recognition accuracy \n									</li>\n						</ul>\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/uface-1-232x300.png\" alt=\"uface-1\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/uface-2-106x300.png\" alt=\"uface-2\" /></figure>			\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/anviz-logo-01-e1588912027597.png\" title=\"anviz logo-01\" alt=\"anviz logo-01\" />											\n		<p>Anviz has been the world’s top provider of biometrics, video surveillance, intelligent smart-home and smart-building solutions with the application of AIoT and cloud technologies since 2001. They promotes the application of AIoT and cloud technologies to provide customers with a more integrated, convenient and efficient smart solution including the best consulting and reliable technical support by their global sales and service network.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"356\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-e1588906193309-1024x356.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Biometric-