algorithm model - ShuffleNet has the capability to empower high accuracy AI algorithm model on Edge analytic devices. The system can be deployed in a very short period of time at public places, realizing temperature screening in a non-contact manner through our AI technology.</p>http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/MEGVII-Mingji-Thermal-Facial-Recognition-Solution.mp4http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/MEGVII-Mingji-Thermal-Facial-Recognition-Solution-1.mp4		\n			<h2>HIGHLIGHTS</h2>		\n		<ul><li>Contactless thermal screening</li><li>Multiple person temperature measurement</li><li>Smooth and fast access</li><li>Visible user-friendly system GUI</li><li>Fever detection alert</li><li>Non-mask detection alert</li><li>100,000 historical records</li><li>+/- 0.1°C accuracy</li></ul>		\n										<img width=\"2560\" height=\"1577\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-scaled.jpg 2560w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-300x185.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-1024x631.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-768x473.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-1536x946.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-2048x1262.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />											\n			<h2>PLUG AND PLAY</h2>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/DeploymentDiagram-01-scaled.jpg\" title=\"DeploymentDiagram-01\" alt=\"DeploymentDiagram-01\" />											\n		<ul><li><strong>Rapid Deployment</strong><p>Installed on edge device, 15 minutes system setup</p></li><li><strong>Optimized Detection Model</strong><p>Optimized forehead detection model for detecting the face of people who wear hats and masks, face detection rate &gt;95%</p></li><li><strong>Non-contact Temperature Measurement</strong><p>Support up to 4 meters in non-contact temperature measurement to ensure epidemic prevention security</p></li><li><strong>Mask-wearing Detection</strong><p>Automatically identify and flag for those who do not wear masks, detection rate &gt;95%</p></li></ul><ul><li><strong>Ultra-precision Temperature Measurement</strong><p>+/- 0.1°C temperature accuracy under 30 - 45 °C environment</p></li><li><strong>AI-Enabled</strong><p>Proprietary algorithm built with neural networks and deep machine learning</p></li><li><strong>Deep Industry Experience</strong><p>MEGVII understands the market challenges and widely deployed in both public and government sectors</p></li></ul>		\n			<h2>CARRY AND GO</h2>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/mingji-dimension-01-1.png\" title=\"mingji-dimension-01\" alt=\"mingji-dimension-01\" />											\n		<ul><li><strong>All in one Backpack</strong><p>The package includes 1 x dual-light camera, 1 x blackbody , 1 x AI processing unit, 1 x Tripod</p></li><li><strong>High Cost Effectiveness</strong><p>Proprietary CNN on edge devices ShuffleNet to bring out best performance on edge devices</p></li></ul><ul><li><strong>Dynamic Temperature Calibration</strong><p>Integrated with blackbody real-time sensing of ambient temperature and dynamically compensates for differences</p></li><li><strong>Temperature Measurement with High Speed Accurate</strong><p>Temperature measurement for 3 ~ 4 people at the same time</p></li></ul>		\n			<h2>UFACE THERMOMETER</h2>		\n		<p>       UFACE Thermometer is a high performance, high reliability and high accuracy face recognition products that support 1:1 and 1:N mode of face recognition. It uses Excelitas Thermal IR Sensors for motion detection, presence monitoring and temperature measurement. The parallel support hold a stable and fast non-contact human body infrared temperature measurement (frontal temperature).</p>		\n			<h2>HIGHLIGHTS</h2>		\n		<ul><li>Fever alarm</li><li>Access control</li><li>Excelitas thermal IR sensors</li><li>Mask detection alert</li><li>Facial recognition</li><li>Wireless connectivity</li><li>Wall mounting, floor stand and turnstile integration</li></ul>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2_Eng-01.png\" title=\"2_Eng-01\" alt=\"2_Eng-01\" />											\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/3-e1589469977912.png\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" />											\n			<h2>FEATURES</h2>		\n		<ul><li>8-inch LCD touch display</li><li>Thermal IR camera</li><li>Wi-Fi interface</li><li>100,000 face database</li><li>Anti-backlight</li><li>Liveness detection</li><li>Non-contact temperature measurement</li><li>Supports recognition with masks</li><li>Supports stranger detection</li><li>Less than 1 second recognition</li><li>99.99% recognition accuracy</li><li>Flexible combination: Face, Thermal, Mask, Card</li></ul>		\n										<img width=\"12500\" height=\"7075\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1.png 12500w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1-300x170.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1-1024x580.png 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1-768x435.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1-1536x869.png 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/¦aµ45¦-01-1-2048x1159.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 12500px) 100vw, 12500px\" />											\n			<h2>Intelligent Management </h2>		\n		<ul><li>Real-time Monitoring</li><li>Personnel and Authorization</li><li>Multi-function Devices</li><li>Time Attentance</li><li>Tool Kit</li><li>Open API</li></ul>		\n			<h2>OTHER SOLUTIONS</h2>		\n			<a href=\"#megvii\" role=\"button\">\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"#anviz\" role=\"button\">\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"#populife\" role=\"button\">\n					</a>\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/MEGVII_LOGO.png\" title=\"megvii\" alt=\"megvii\" />											\n		<p>       MEGVII is a world-class AI company with core competencies in deep learning. Headquartered in Beijing with over 2,000 employees, MEGVII maintains four research and development centers in China (Beijing, Shanghai, Nanjing and Chengdu). MEGVII provides fullstack solutions, which encompass algorithms, software and AI-empowered IoT devices, to customers and has achieved leading positions across multiple industries.</p>		\n			<h2>MEGVII Personal IOT</h2>		\n		       MEGVII Personal IoT solutions comprise algorithms and software applications. Facial recognition-based device security solutions allow users to conveniently unlock their devices, and the computational photography solutions allow consumers to take pictures or videos with quality comparable to those taken using professional single-lens reflex cameras.		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/PersonalIoT-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/PersonalIoT-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/PersonalIoT-1024x1024.png 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/PersonalIoT-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/PersonalIoT-768x768.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/PersonalIoT.png 1398w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h2>MEGVII City IOT</h2>		\n		<p>       MEGVII City IoT solutions comprise algorithms, platform software, application software and hardware products. The smart city management solutions are designed to enhance