algorithm model - ShuffleNet has the capability to empower high accuracy AI algorithm model on Edge analytic devices. The system can be deployed in a very short period of time at public places, realizing temperature screening in a non-contact manner through our AI technology.</p>http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/MEGVII-Mingji-Thermal-Facial-Recognition-Solution.mp4http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/MEGVII-Mingji-Thermal-Facial-Recognition-Solution-1.mp4		\n			<h2>HIGHLIGHTS</h2>		\n		<ul><li>Contactless thermal screening</li><li>Multiple person temperature measurement</li><li>Smooth and fast access</li><li>Visible user-friendly system GUI</li><li>Fever detection alert</li><li>Non-mask detection alert</li><li>100,000 historical records</li><li>+/- 0.1°C accuracy</li></ul>		\n										<img width=\"2560\" height=\"1577\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-scaled.jpg 2560w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-300x185.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-1024x631.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-768x473.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-1536x946.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Thermal-Screening-1-2048x1262.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />											\n			<h2>PLUG AND PLAY</h2>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/DeploymentDiagram-01-scaled.jpg\" title=\"DeploymentDiagram-01\" alt=\"DeploymentDiagram-01\" />											\n		<ul><li><strong>Rapid Deployment</strong><p>Installed on edge device, 15 minutes system setup</p></li><li><strong>Optimized Detection Model</strong><p>Optimized forehead detection model